            <div class="header">
                <h1>About us</h1>
                <h2>What RestaurantIO can do for you</h2>
            </div>

            <div class="content">
                <h2 class="content-subhead">What we do</h2>
                <p>
                    RestaurantIO is a point of service system for restaurants. We provide an easy way for restaurants
                    to take orders, manage tables, bill processing and a reporting tool to give useful information.
                </p>

                <h2 class="content-subhead">Menu</h2>
                <p>
                    Our menu page is fully customizable allowing the administrator to alter menu items, prices, allow
                    for different filtering of items.
                    Giving your staff an easy and quick way to enter your customers orders!
                    <div class="pure-g">
                        <div class="pure-u-24-24">
                            <img class="pure-img" src="/content/images/menuSample.PNG" alt="Menu page sample">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </p>

                <h2 class="content-subhead">Tables</h2>
                <p>
                    Our tables page is fully customizable allowing the administrator to alter the layout, table patron amount,
                    allowing tables to have different states from occupied, reserved, dirty.
                    Giving your staff an easy way to keep track of what is happening in the restaurant!
                    <div class="pure-g">
                        <div class="pure-u-24-24">
                            <img class="pure-img" src="/content/images/tableSample.PNG" alt="Table page sample">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </p>

                <h2 class="content-subhead">Bills</h2>
                <p>
                    Our bills page displays all bills entered from the menu page, this allows you to keep an eye on everything 
                    that you have going on, quickly print receipts, remove items.
                    <div class="pure-g">
                        <div class="pure-u-24-24">
                            <img class="pure-img" src="/content/images/billSample.PNG" alt="Bill page sample">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </p>

                <h2 class="content-subhead">Reports</h2>
                <p>
                    Our bills page allows the restaurant administrator to print reports detailing crucial information from
                    daily, monthly, and yearly cash summary, menu popularity, server incomes, popular times of day  
                    <div class="pure-g">
                        <div class="pure-u-24-24">
                            <img class="pure-img" src="/content/images/reportSample.PNG" alt="Bill page sample">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </p>
            </div>
